--           fix-pass count, and first-pass miss count per cube. Prints a
--           final aligned comparison table (Cube | BPS | Time | Passes |
--           1st Misses) plus a trend line identifying the first BPS where
--           fix passes were needed. btn label updates per-cube and during
--           each fix pass to show live progress.
